         <li>
          <b> Pubbelly Noodle Bar</b> <dd>Come to this exposed-brick gastropub with Asian-fusion tapas featuring pork paired with craft beer and wine!</dd>
         </li>
         <li>
          <b>Micheal's Genuine Food and Drink</b> <dd>A new American eatery with locally sourced foods and inventive deserts!</dd>
         </li>
         <li>
         <b>Zuma</b> <dd>Come to this chic and minimalist Japanese hot spot overlooking the Miami River and enjoy shared dishes, sushi and more!</dd>
         </li>
         <li>
         <b>Joe's Stone Crab</b> <dd>This Cavernous bustling space is exclusively open between October and May, with crowds drawing in to eat some delicious crab and key-lime pie!</dd>
         </li>
         <li>
          <b>Alter</b> <dd>Refined new American foods served in an open industrial setting with an open kitchen and a lovely garden!</dd>
         </li>
       </ul>
     </p>
